name: Rapunzel
subtitle: Gifted Artist
author: Aubrey Archer

additional_info.title: FAQ 1
additional_info.body:
Q: Three of my characters have 2 damage each on them. If my Rapunzel- Gifted Artist sings Hakuna Matata in that situation, how many cards can I draw with her Let Your Power Shine ability?

A: 3 cards. Rapunzel- Gifted Artistâ€™s ability triggers for each individual character of yours that has damage removed from them regardless of how much damage is removed from that character.

rules_text: Shift 3 (You may pay 3 to play this on top of one of your characters named Rapunzel.) LET YOUR POWER SHINE Whenever you remove 1 or more damage from one of your characters, you may draw a card.
